WEBVTT

00:00:00.771 --> 00:00:13.482 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah knows just what we need
To bring us joy and to succeed.

00:00:13.482 --> 00:00:26.569 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So he provides so many ways
In which to serve and spend our days.

00:00:26.569 --> 00:00:37.988 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Reaching out, giving all,
for our God above.

00:00:37.988 --> 00:00:51.284 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And where the need is great, there we’ll be,
reaching out in love.

00:00:51.284 --> 00:01:04.245 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There’s work to do in ev’ry land.
Where there’s a need, we lend a hand.

00:01:04.245 --> 00:01:17.499 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
By reaching out, we show we care.
We want to help and want to share.

00:01:17.499 --> 00:01:28.918 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Reaching out, giving all,
for our God above.

00:01:28.918 --> 00:01:42.255 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And where the need is great, there we’ll be,
reaching out in love.

00:01:42.255 --> 00:01:54.883 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And here at home, in towns nearby,
We plan, we build, new skills we try.

00:01:54.883 --> 00:02:08.220 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We learn to speak a foreign tongue
And bring good news to ev’ryone.

00:02:08.220 --> 00:02:19.640 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Reaching out, giving all,
for our God above.

